 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; width: 80px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\"><span>一级缓存</span></td>\r\n            <td style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">4&times;128KB</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr bgcolor=\"#ffffff\" style=\"padding-bottom: 5px; padding-left: 5px; padding-right: 5px; padding-top: 5px\">\r\n            <td style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; width: 80px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\"><span>二级缓存</span></td>\r\n            <td style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">4MB</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr style=\"padding-bottom: 5px; padding-left: 5px; padding-right: 5px; padding-top: 5px\">\r\n            <td colspan=\"2\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; background-color: rgb(242,247,253); margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\"><b>技术参数</b></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr bgcolor=\"#ffffff\" style=\"padding-bottom: 5px; padding-left: 5px; padding-right: 5px; padding-top: 5px\">\r\n            <td style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; width: 80px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\"><span>指令集</span></td>\r\n            <td style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">MMX（+），3DNow!，SSE（1,2,3,4A），X86-64，AMD-V</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr bgcolor=\"#ffffff\" style=\"padding-bottom: 5px; padding-left: 5px; padding-right: 5px; padding-top: 5px\">\r\n            <td style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; width: 80px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\"><span>内存控制器</span></td>\r\n            <td style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">DDR3-1866</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(245,248,253); text-indent: 0px; margin: 15px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); border-left-width: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 就在今年前半年，500元市场还是双核争霸的局面，到如今AMD彻底改变了这一切！就在这几天AMD拿出了旗下一款基于FM1接口的超实惠四核产品，AthlonⅡX4 631 ！这是市售唯一一款低于500元的四核32nm产品，可以说凭借着物理四核心的优势完全傲视了一把现在的入门级双核产品。其意义不仅仅是让那些预算有限的玩家体验到四核的快感，更是极大的弥补了FM1接口平台的价位空档，这无疑是AMD今秋的一把杀手锏。评测室最近收到了这款CPU，那么接下来就是我为大家带来的评测。</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(245,248,253); text-indent: 0px; margin: 15px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); border-left-width: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><img alt=\"最具性价比的Llano速龙ⅡX4631抢先测\" style=\"border-bottom: rgb(0,0,0) 1px solid; border-left: rgb(0,0,0) 1px solid; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; vertical-align: top; border-top: rgb(0,0,0) 1px solid; border-right: rgb(0,0,0) 1px solid; padding-top: 0px\" src=\"http://img04.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i4/21939609/T2odr_XdhXXXXXXXXX_!!21939609.jpg\" /><br />\r\n▲32nm FM1 Athlon ⅡX4 631评测</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left; padding-bottom: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(245,248,253); text-indent: 0px; margin: 15px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); border-left-width: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">　　新的FM1接口Athlon ⅡX4 631是最新推出的一款CPU，相比原来的 AM3接口Athlon ⅡX4 640 、Athlon ⅡX4 645，新的32nm工艺制成的Athlon ⅡX4 631不仅拥有更低的电压，更低的功耗，价格上也是够劲爆，只卖499元！这无疑拉近了物理多核处理器与用户的距离，加速了四核处理器的普及。</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(245,248,253); text-indent: 0px; margin: 15px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); border-left-width: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><img alt=\"最具性价比的Llano速龙ⅡX4631抢先测\" style=\"border-bottom: rgb(0,0,0) 1px solid; border-left: rgb(0,0,0) 1px solid; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; vertical-align: top; border-top: rgb(0,0,0) 1px solid; border-right: rgb(0,0,0) 1px solid; padding-top: 0px\" src=\"http://img04.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i4/21939609/T2TUz8XfxaXXXXXXXX_!!21939609.jpg\" /><br />\r\n▲CPU-Z截图</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left; padding-bottom: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(245,248,253); text-indent: 0px; margin: 15px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); border-left-width: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">　　Athlon ⅡX4 631，主频2.6GHz，外频100MHz，倍频x26，默认电压1.360V，拥有4x4的1024KB二级缓存，相比于前代有了翻倍的提升！新的Athlon基于Llano代号，因此同APU一样采用了32nm制程工艺，相比原来的45nm产品更加节能高效。从规格上来讲这款CPU超过了前代不少，而且个人认为凭借着高倍频，低外频的特性，超频空间应该很大。</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(245,248,253); text-indent: 0px; margin: 15px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); border-left-width: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><img alt=\"最具性价比的Llano速龙ⅡX4631抢先测\" style=\"border-bottom: rgb(0,0,0) 1px solid; border-left: rgb(0,0,0) 1px solid; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; vertical-align: top; border-top: rgb(0,0,0) 1px solid; border-right: rgb(0,0,0) 1px solid; padding-top: 0px\" src=\"http://img01.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i1/21939609/T2GRn9XhxXXXXXXXXX_!!21939609.jpg\" /><br />\r\n▲Athlon ⅡX4 631</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(245,248,253); text-indent: 0px; margin: 15px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); border-left-width: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><b>AthlonⅡX4 631优化后的K10</b></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(245,248,253); text-indent: 0px; margin: 15px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); border-left-width: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">　　从CPU-Z的截图我们我可以看到，新的AthlonⅡX4 631的二级缓存扩大了一倍，CPU核心采用了Llano上面针对K10优化的&ldquo;STARS&rdquo;架构<span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: black; font-size: 10.5pt\">，即<span>Husky</span>微构架</span>，应该说优化后的架构除了一些规格上的提升，能效上也必然会有体现。</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center; padding-bottom: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(245,248,253); text-indent: 0px; margin: 15px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); border-left-width: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><b><img alt=\"最具性价比的Llano速龙ⅡX4631抢先测\" width=\"500\" height=\"240\" style=\"border-bottom: rgb(0,0,0) 1px solid; border-left: rgb(0,0,0) 1px solid; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; vertical-align: top; border-top: rgb(0,0,0) 1px solid; border-right: rgb(0,0,0) 1px solid; padding-top: 0px\" src=\"http://img01.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i1/21939609/T2vY__Xe4XXXXXXXXX_!!21939609.jpg\" /><br />\r\n</b>▲STARS微构架</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(245,248,253); text-indent: 0px; margin: 15px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); border-left-width: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">　　Husky微构架主要的提升如下：</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(245,248,253); text-indent: 0px; margin: 15px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); border-left-width: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">　　1、采用了先进的32nm制造工艺</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(245,248,253); text-indent: 0px; margin: 15px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); border-left-width: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">　　2、增强了每周期指令数大约6%，提高了二级缓存的容量</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(245,248,253); text-indent: 0px; margin: 15px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); border-left-width: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">　　首先AMD在制程向前迈进了一步，32nm的工艺有效减少了CPU沟槽的漏电率和驱动电流，使得&ldquo;速龙&rdquo;更加节能。另外基于(Instruction Pointer，指令指示器)的HW Prefetcher(硬件预读器)设计被重新改进、Reorder缓冲器容量提高了20%、Load/Store单元的缓冲器容量直接翻倍，新增硬件除法器等使得周期操作数(IPC)有了一个6%的提升。</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(245,248,253); text-indent: 0px; margin: 15px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); border-left-width: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">　　另外一点值得提的是，新的<span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: black; font-size: 10.5pt\">32nm</span>版AthlonⅡX4 631中集成的内存控制器和APU中的完全一样，默认支持DDR3 1866MHz，这不仅提高了系统的带宽，同时也为超频预留了更大的空间。</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(245,248,253); text-indent: 0px; margin: 15px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); border-left-width: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><b>市场定位与价格分析</b></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(245,248,253); text-indent: 0px; margin: 15px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); border-left-width: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">　　按命名规则来讲新的AthlonⅡX4 631应该是替代AthlonⅡX4 630级别的产品的，定位应当属于入门四核平台，是专门针对独显用户使用的四核独立CPU。目前来看新的AthlonⅡX4 631是用来填补FM1接口无低端处理器的市场空白的，因为目前定位主流的A6、A8处理器在更高位置，所以FM1接口主板上正好有一个500元的空档，AthlonⅡX4 631的出现填补了这个空档，同时会进一步加速推进物理四核平台的普及。</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(245,248,253); text-indent: 0px; margin: 15px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); border-left-width: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">　　当下500元的市场主要还是双（三）核产品为主包括AMD Athlon II &times;3 445(速龙II三核)，Intel的PentiumG、 E 6x00系列等，AthlonⅡX4 631的出现必将会对这些双核产品产生很大影响。因为其综合性能足以媲美Core i3 2100以上价位的产品。</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(245,248,253); text-indent: 0px; margin: 15px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); border-left-width: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><img alt=\"最具性价比的Llano速龙ⅡX4631抢先测\" style=\"border-bottom: rgb(0,0,0) 1px solid; border-left: rgb(0,0,0) 1px solid; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; vertical-align: top; border-top: rgb(0,0,0) 1px solid; border-right: rgb(0,0,0) 1px solid; padding-top: 0px\" src=\"http://img02.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i2/21939609/T2ckD9XjdXXXXXXXXX_!!21939609.jpg\" /><br />\r\n▲PentiumG、E6x00、AMD Athlon II &times;3 445(速龙II三核)</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left; padding-bottom: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(245,248,253); text-indent: 0px; margin: 15px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); border-left-width: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">　　而在搭配的主板方面，支持FM1接口的A75和A55也更具性价比，目前很多一二线厂商都有500左右的A75出现，而且随着APU的出货和产品线的丰富，预计在接下来的几个月，AMD的FM1接口主板将有一个很大的市场需求，因此如果现在要购买一块AMD芯片组主板的话，A75和A55是明智之举。</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(245,248,253); text-indent: 0px; margin: 15px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); border-left-width: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><b>AthlonⅡX4 631测试平台</b></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(245,248,253); text-indent: 0px; margin: 15px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); border-left-width: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>\r\n<table cellspacing=\"1\" cellpadding=\"5\" width=\"500\" bgcolor=\"#666666\" align=\"center\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(245,248,253); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-spacing: 0px; padding-right: 0px; border-collapse: collapse; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align: center; padding-bottom: 0px; line-height: 16px; background-color: rgb(183,184,186); margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; color: rgb(255,255,255); font-size: 14px; font-weight: bold; padding-top: 0px\">测试平台信息</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n      