INSERT INTO necs_goods VALUES('3532','419','ECS003532','讯景 HD7850 2G 魔将','+','86','0','','100','0.000','0.00','1199.00','0.00','0','0','1','XFX7850 XFX785A-CEF5 双风扇 大卡 大板 畅销 特价 性价比','','<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://img03.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i3/12875414/T2YvcpXk0XXXXXXXXX_!!12875414.jpg\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; word-spacing: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; text-transform: none; color: rgb(64,64,64); text-indent: 0px; padding-top: 0px; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-align: center; widows: 2; orphans: 2; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;&nbsp; 众所周知，对于《古墓丽影9》、《孤岛危机》这些对<a style=\"color: rgb(51,102,204); text-decoration: none\">显卡</a>要求较高的主流游戏大作来说，想在高画质下流畅运行它们，<a style=\"color: rgb(51,102,204); text-decoration: none\">显卡</a>除了本身的核心性能外，显存容量和显存位宽也是十分重要的。<a style=\"color: rgb(51,102,204); text-decoration: none\">1GB</a>&nbsp;<a style=\"color: rgb(51,102,204); text-decoration: none\">128bit</a>的<a style=\"color: rgb(51,102,204); text-decoration: none\">HD7770</a>显然是不能满足条件的，那么如何才能畅玩《古墓丽影9》呢？今天笔者给大家介绍的这款讯景<a style=\"color: rgb(51,102,204); text-decoration: none\">HD7850魔将</a>2G双风扇显卡就可以轻松为你解决这个难题，该显卡目前新上市，游戏性能十分出色。</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; word-spacing: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; text-transform: none; color: rgb(64,64,64); text-indent: 0px; padding-top: 0px; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-align: center; widows: 2; orphans: 2; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><img id=\"content-first-img\" height=\"313\" alt=\"讯景HD7850魔将2G双风扇新品上市\" width=\"500\" style=\"border-right: black 0px solid; border-top: black 0px solid; vertical-align: top; border-left: black 0px solid; border-bottom: black 0px solid\" src=\"http://2e.zol-img.com.cn/product/114_500x2000/54/ce5HG8vD7CKuw.jpg\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; word-spacing: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; text-transform: none; color: rgb(64,64,64); text-indent: 0px; padding-top: 0px; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-align: center; widows: 2; orphans: 2; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">（讯景<a style=\"color: rgb(51,102,204); text-decoration: none\">HD7850</a>魔将2G双风扇）</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; word-spacing: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; text-transform: none; color: rgb(64,64,64); text-indent: 0px; padding-top: 0px; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); widows: 2; orphans: 2; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">　　讯景HD7850魔将2G双风扇采用GCN架构设计的Pitcairn&nbsp;Pro图形核心，基于先进的28nm制程工艺制造，拥有1024个流<a style=\"color: rgb(51,102,204); text-decoration: none\">处理器</a>，显卡频率设定为860MHz/4800MHz，与公版保持一致，显卡支持PCI-E3.0传输标准和<a style=\"color: rgb(51,102,204); text-decoration: none\">DX11</a>.1特效。显卡显存为2G双风扇&nbsp;DDR5，搭配<a style=\"color: rgb(51,102,204); text-decoration: none\">256bit</a>大显存位宽使得显卡游戏性能出色，玩家可以高画质流畅玩《古墓丽影9》等主流单机游戏！</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; word-spacing: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; text-transform: none; color: rgb(64,64,64); text-indent: 0px; padding-top: 0px; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-align: center; widows: 2; orphans: 2; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><img height=\"313\" alt=\"讯景HD7850魔将2G双风扇新品上市\" width=\"500\" style=\"border-right: black 0px solid; border-top: black 0px solid; vertical-align: top; border-left: black 0px solid; border-bottom: black 0px solid\" src=\"http://2c.zol-img.com.cn/product/114_500x2000/64/cesPpDSd2OeBk.jpg\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; word-spacing: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; text-transform: none; color: rgb(64,64,64); text-indent: 0px; padding-top: 0px; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-align: center; widows: 2; orphans: 2; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">（PCB背板）</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; word-spacing: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; text-transform: none; color: rgb(64,64,64); text-indent: 0px; padding-top: 0px; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); widows: 2; orphans: 2; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">　　讯景HD7850魔将2G双风扇采用非公版设计的PCB板，全固态电容加全封闭的电感，用料高端，显卡工作更加稳定。更长的PCB板也提供了更大的散热面积，显卡散热得到优化。</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; word-spacing: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; text-transform: none; color: rgb(64,64,64); text-indent: 0px; padding-top: 0px; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-align: center; widows: 2; orphans: 2; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><img height=\"313\" alt=\"讯景HD7850魔将2G双风扇新品上市\" width=\"500\" style=\"border-right: black 0px solid; border-top: black 0px solid; vertical-align: top; border-left: black 0px solid; border-bottom: black 0px solid\" src=\"http://2f.zol-img.com.cn/product/114_500x2000/73/ceFenlNvmDnO.jpg\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; word-spacing: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; text-transform: none; color: rgb(64,64,64); text-indent: 0px; padding-top: 0px; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-align: center; widows: 2; orphans: 2; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">（风扇）</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; word-spacing: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; text-transform: none; color: rgb(64,64,64); text-indent: 0px; padding-top: 0px; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); widows: 2; orphans: 2; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">　　散热方面，讯景HD7850魔将2G双风扇采用了2个高档的双滚珠轴承风扇，直径更是达到了10cm。再搭载上大面积的散热铝板和2根大尺寸热管，组成了整个显卡强劲的散热系统。面对高温的夏天，显卡有了良好的散热保障。</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; word-spacing: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; text-transform: none; color: rgb(64,64,64); text-indent: 0px; padding-top: 0px; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-align: center; widows: 2; orphans: 2; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><img height=\"313\" alt=\"讯景HD7850魔将2G双风扇新品上市\" width=\"500\" style=\"border-right: black 0px solid; border-top: black 0px solid; vertical-align: top; border-left: black 0px solid; border-bottom: black 0px solid\" src=\"http://2f.zol-img.com.cn/product/114_500x2000/79/cexcR1ug2xCI2.jpg\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; word-spacing: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; text-transform: none; color: rgb(64,64,64); text-indent: 0px; padding-top: 0px; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-align: center; widows: 2; orphans: 2; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">（供电）</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; word-spacing: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; text-transform: none; color: rgb(64,64,64); text-indent: 0px; padding-top: 0px; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); widows: 2; orphans: 2; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">　　供电方面，讯景HD7850魔将2G双风扇提供了双6Pin外接供电接口，采用高端电容电感和超合金mos管，显卡供电转换效率高，给显卡核心运行在高频上提供了充分的保障，保证高频下长时间的稳定工作，同时为玩家超频提供了更好的基础。</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; word-spacing: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; text-transform: none; color: rgb(64,64,64); text-indent: 0px; padding-top: 0px; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-align: center; widows: 2; orphans: 2; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><img height=\"313\" alt=\"讯景HD7850魔将2G双风扇新品上市\" width=\"500\" style=\"border-right: black 0px solid; border-top: black 0px solid; vertical-align: top; border-left: black 0px solid; border-bottom: black 0px solid\" src=\"http://2c.zol-img.com.cn/product/114_500x2000/88/ceb2TE2dVfkw.jpg\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; word-spacing: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; text-transform: none; color: rgb(64,64,64); text-indent: 0px; padding-top: 0px; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-align: center; widows: 2; orphans: 2; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">输出接口）</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; word-spacing: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; text-transform: none; color: rgb(64,64,64); text-indent: 0px; padding-top: 0px; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); widows: 2; orphans: 2; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">　　输出接口方面，讯景HD7850魔将2G双风扇提供了2个DVI接口和1个HDMI接口以及2个Mini&nbsp;DP高清接口，配合AMD&nbsp;Eyefinity多屏显示输出技术，为用户组建多屏系统提供有力保障。</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; word-spacing: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; text-transform: none; color: rgb(64,64,64); text-indent: 0px; padding-top: 0px; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); widows: 2; orphans: 2; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">　　讯景在2013年针对不同级别的游戏玩家推出的魔族系列显卡，包括四个系列，由高至低分别是：魔神、魔尊、魔将以及魔灵。魔族系列显卡采用了全新的包装，应用讯景优化后独有的散热系统，以及使用更加优秀的<a style=\"color: rgb(51,102,204); text-decoration: none\">产品</a>做工，它们都将赋予游戏玩家们更好的产品体验；同时魔族系列的显卡定位将更加符合不同级别游戏玩家的需求，相比同级别显卡在性能上有很大的提高，适合玩家选购。</p>\r\n<p><br class=\"Apple-interchange-newline\" />\r\n&nbsp;</p>','images/201307/thumb_img/3532_thumb_G_1373090139089.jpg','images/201307/goods_img/3532_G_1373090139190.jpg','images/201307/source_img/3532_G_1373090139837.jpg','1','','1','1','0','0','1372902874','100','0','0','0','0','0','0','1376016827','5','','0','0','0','');
