INSERT INTO necs_goods VALUES('3583','571','ECS003583','尼康14-24','+','42','23','','100','0.000','13560.00','11300.00','0.00','0','0','1','超广角 大光圈 14-24','','<h1 style=\"padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; font: bold 26px/34px 微软雅黑; text-transform: none; color: rgb(34,34,34); text-indent: 0px; padding-top: 0px; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(245,248,253); text-align: center; orphans: 2; widows: 2; webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">超广角大光圈 尼康14-24 F2.8售11300元</h1>\r\n<p style=\"padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 14px 0px; word-spacing: 0px; font: 14px/25px simsun; text-transform: none; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-indent: 0px; padding-top: 0px; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(245,248,253); orphans: 2; widows: 2; webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <a class=\"hui14_line\" href=\"http://detail.zol.com.cn/lens_index/subcate268_657_list_1.html\" style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0); border-bottom: rgb(255,79,79) 1px dashed\">尼康</a>AF-S 14-24mm/F2.8 ED<a class=\"hui14_line\" href=\"http://detail.zol.com.cn/lens_index/subcate268_list_1.html\" style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0); border-bottom: rgb(255,79,79) 1px dashed\">镜头</a>是一支十分出色的超广角镜头，这支纳米镀膜镜头是尼康Fans必买的一支神镜，本身光学结构出色之余还为数码单反做出了优化。<br clear=\"all\" style=\"font-size: 0px; line-height: 0\" />\r\n<img onclick=\"window.open(\'http://detail.zol.com.cn/picture_index_274/index2737851.shtml\');\" height=\"375\" alt=\"超广角大光圈 尼康14-24 F2.8售13100元 \" src=\"http://2d.zol-img.com.cn/product/27_500x2000/851/ce8QpQCjvU7Ts.jpg\" width=\"500\" style=\"border-right: black 1px solid; border-top: black 1px solid; border-left: black 1px solid; cursor: pointer; border-bottom: black 1px solid\" /><br />\r\n<b>尼康 AF-S Nikkor 24-70mm f/2.8G</b></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 14px 0px; word-spacing: 0px; font: 14px/25px simsun; text-transform: none; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-indent: 0px; padding-top: 0px; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(245,248,253); orphans: 2; widows: 2; webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">　　随着尼康全画幅数码单反D3的发布，尼康也推出尼克尔AF-S 14-24mm f/2.8G ED这样一只有点变态的镜头。虽然14-24/2.8在全画幅变焦镜头里面不是最广的一只（<a class=\"hui14_line\" href=\"http://detail.zol.com.cn/lens_index/subcate268_1799_list_1.html\" style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0); border-bottom: rgb(255,79,79) 1px dashed\">适马</a>有12-24mm F4.5-5.6 EX DG ASP HSM），但是尼康把F2.8的焦段推进到14mm的领域，并且14-24mm焦段内实现了恒定F2.8光圈，也算是一个创举。</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 14px 0px; word-spacing: 0px; font: 14px/25px simsun; text-transform: none; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-indent: 0px; padding-top: 0px; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(245,248,253); orphans: 2; widows: 2; webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><a href=\"http://detail.zol.com.cn/picture_index_274/index2737850.shtml\" style=\"color: rgb(19,75,160); text-decoration: underline\"><img height=\"375\" alt=\"超广角大光圈 尼康14-24 F2.8售13100元 \" src=\"http://2c.zol-img.com.cn/product/27_500x2000/850/cemJNgUunrgcU.jpg\" width=\"500\" style=\"border-right: black 1px solid; border-top: black 1px solid; border-left: black 1px solid; border-bottom: black 1px solid\" /></a><br />\r\n<b><b>尼康 AF-S Nikkor 24-70mm f/2.8G</b></b></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 14px 0px; word-spacing: 0px; font: 14px/25px simsun; text-transform: none; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-indent: 0px; padding-top: 0px; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(245,248,253); orphans: 2; widows: 2; webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">　　尼康尼克尔AF-S 14-24mm f/2.8G ED这一新变焦镜头具有一系列专业特性，可提供优越的整体性能。除了所有的焦距具有稳定的最大光圈 f/2.8之外，在18-24 mm焦距时，这种镜头还具有 0.28 m/0.9 ft 的较短的最近主体对焦距离。这款镜头特别适合用于新闻摄影工作和一般的拍照需求。</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 14px 0px; word-spacing: 0px; font: 14px/25px simsun; text-transform: none; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-indent: 0px; padding-top: 0px; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(245,248,253); orphans: 2; widows: 2; webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><a href=\"http://detail.zol.com.cn/picture_index_274/index2737849.shtml\" style=\"color: rgb(204,0,0); text-decoration: underline\"><img height=\"375\" alt=\"超广角大光圈 尼康14-24 F2.8售13100元 \" src=\"http://2b.zol-img.com.cn/product/27_500x2000/849/ceWJChXZwPjMU.jpg\" width=\"500\" style=\"border-right: black 1px solid; border-top: black 1px solid; border-left: black 1px solid; border-bottom: black 1px solid\" /></a><br />\r\n<b><b><b>尼康 AF-S Nikkor 24-70mm f/2.8G</b></b></b></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 14px 0px; word-spacing: 0px; font: 14px/25px simsun; text-transform: none; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-indent: 0px; padding-top: 0px; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(245,248,253); orphans: 2; widows: 2; webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">　　AF-S 尼克尔 14-24mm F2.8 G ED的最伟大之处在于，这是一只用于全画幅的超广角镜头，这使在此之前那些DX画幅的11-18或者12-24镜头显得不值一提。它是支援FX Format的大口径超广角镜头，等效焦距就是自身标称的14-24mm，光圈值却可达到F2.8，这样的指标是为目前的世界之最。另外，也采用了号称世界最大的全玻璃非球面镜片。当该镜头使用在DX 幅面的DSLR时，焦点距离约相当于21-36mm。</p>','images/201307/thumb_img/3583_thumb_G_1373179398704.jpg','images/201307/goods_img/3583_G_1373179398399.jpg','images/201307/source_img/3583_G_1373179398623.png','1','','1','1','0','113','1373179398','100','0','0','0','0','0','0','1373179398','58','','-1','-1','0','');
