晰高清，画质升级</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; word-spacing: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; text-transform: none; color: rgb(64,64,64); text-indent: 0px; padding-top: 0px; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); orphans: 2; widows: 2; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">灵晰高清 画质升级<img title=\"\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-right: 0px; padding-right: 0px; border-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; float: none; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: top; border-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; border-bottom: 0px\" src=\"http://www.samsung.com/cn/consumer-images/product/monitors/2013/LS24C350HL-XF/features/LS24C350HL-XF-84-0.jpg\" /><br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"word-spacing: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; text-transform: none; color: rgb(64,64,64); text-indent: 0px; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); orphans: 2; widows: 2; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">灵晰高清功能可以直接对图片进行专业处理，增强图像品质，避免因放大操作而造成的图像品质下降的问题，同时在笔记本双屏显示处理时，色彩更加鲜活、艳丽，让您获得更加清晰、明锐的画面。</div>\r\n<div style=\"word-spacing: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; text-transform: none; color: rgb(64,64,64); text-indent: 0px; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); orphans: 2; widows: 2; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">\r\n<h2 style=\"padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; font-weight: bold; font-size: 1.5em; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0.83em 0px; padding-top: 0px\">控制功耗 轻松节能</h2>\r\n<img title=\"\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-right: 0px; border-top: 0px; vertical-align: top; border-left: 0px; border-bottom: 0px\" src=\"http://www.samsung.com/cn/consumer-images/product/monitors/2013/LS24C350HL-XF/features/LS24C350HL-XF-90-0.jpg\" /><br />\r\n<div>&ldquo;灵惠节能&rdquo;为您轻松节约能耗。它有三种节能模式供您选择(节电25%、50%和功能关闭),你完全可以根据个人需要选择屏幕亮度。三星的节能承诺由您与环境一同见证。降低50%的能耗让您真正做到绿色环保。三星&ldquo;灵惠节能&rdquo;助您实现节能梦想。</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"word-spacing: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; text-transform: none; color: rgb(64,64,64); text-indent: 0px; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); orphans: 2; widows: 2; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">\r\n<h2 style=\"padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; font-weight: bold; font-size: 1.5em; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0.83em 0px; padding-top: 0px\">完美兼容 Windows8</h2>\r\n<img title=\"\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-right: 0px; border-top: 0px; vertical-align: top; border-left: 0px; border-bottom: 0px\" src=\"http://www.samsung.com/cn/consumer-images/product/monitors/2013/LS24C350HL-XF/features/LS24C350HL-XF-77-0.jpg\" /><br />\r\n<div>此款显示器获得了Windows 8 认证标识，可完美兼容Windows 8，并且支持Metro用户界面。</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"word-spacing: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; text-transform: none; color: rgb(64,64,64); text-indent: 0px; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); orphans: 2; widows: 2; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">\r\n<div>\r\n<h2 style=\"padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; font-weight: bold; font-size: 1.5em; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0.83em 0px; padding-top: 0px\">外观与功能 完美兼具</h2>\r\n<img title=\"\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-right: 0px; border-top: 0px; vertical-align: top; border-left: 0px; border-bottom: 0px\" src=\"http://www.samsung.com/cn/consumer-images/product/monitors/2013/LS24C350HL-XF/features/LS24C350HL-XF-38-0.jpg\" /><br />\r\n<div>此款显示器拥有高光泽时尚外观设计，简约精致；独具建筑学美感的支架还可以优化空间，让您工作更加高效。</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h2 style=\"padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; font-weight: bold; font-size: 1.5em; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0.83em 0px; padding-top: 0px\">环保认证-能源之星</h2>\r\n<img title=\"\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-right: 0px; border-top: 0px; vertical-align: top; border-left: 0px; border-bottom: 0px\" src=\"http://www.samsung.com/cn/consumer-images/product/monitors/2013/LS24C350HL-XF/features/LS24C350HL-XF-55-0.jpg\" /><br />\r\n<div>三星显示器已通过能源之星的评级认可，能最大限度降低企业成本。其超低的功耗完美地满足了企业经营和环境保护的需求。</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"word-spacing: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; text-transform: none; color: rgb(64,64,64); text-indent: 0px; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); orphans: 2; widows: 2; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">特征和规格如有更动，恕不另行通知</div>\r\n<p style=\"padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; word-spacing: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; text-transform: none; color: rgb(64,64,64); text-indent: 0px; padding-top: 0px; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); orphans: 2; widows: 2; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"border-top-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; text-transform: none; color: rgb(64,64,64); text-indent: 0px; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); border-right-width: 0px; orphans: 2; widows: 2; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">\r\n<p style=\"padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; line-height: 1.4; padding-top: 0px\"><img title=\"S24C350HL的尺寸\" alt=\"S24C350HL的尺寸\" style=\"border-right: 0px; padding-right: 0px; border-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; float: none; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: top; border-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; border-bottom: 0px\" src=\"http://www.samsung.com/cn/consumer-images/product/monitors/2013/LS24C350HL-XF/LS24C350HL-XF-31117-0.jpg\" /></p>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"word-spacing: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; text-transform: none; color: rgb(64,64,64); text-indent: 0px; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); orphans: 2; widows: 2; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">\r\n<div>\r\n<h2 style=\"padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; font-weight: bold; font-size: 1.5em; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0.83em 0px; padding-top: 0px\">显示</h2>\r\n<ul style=\"padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 40px; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 1em 1em 1em 0px; padding-top: 0px; list-style-type: none\">\r\n    <li style=\"padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; list-style-position: outside; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; list-style-type: disc\">屏幕尺寸:23.6&quot;(16:9)</li>\r\n    <li style=\"padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; list-style-position: outside; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; list-style-type: disc\">类型:LED 背光</li>\r\n    <li style=\"padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; list-style-position: outside; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; list-style-type: disc\">亮度:250cd/㎡</li>\r\n    <li style=\"padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; list-style-position: outside; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; list-style-type: disc\">对比度:Mega DCR</li>\r\n    <li style=\"padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; list-style-position: outside; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; list-style-type: disc\">分辩率:1920 x 1080</li>\r\n    <li style=\"padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; list-style-position: outside; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; list-style-type: disc\">响应时间:5ms</li>\r\n    <li style=\"padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; list-style-position: outside; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-top: 0px; list-style-type: disc\">可视角度(水平/垂直):170&deg;/160&deg;(CR&gt;10)</li>\r\n    <li style=\"padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; list-style-posit